#doc (Page) "RISC-V zkVM Track" =>

Verify the arithmetization of RISC-V zkVMs. Ensure polynomial constraints exactly encode RISC-V instruction semantics based on the official Sail RISC-V specification.

# Direction

This track is where documentation about zkVM-specific verification work can expand over time. In the current rewrite, it serves as the stable landing page for future additions such as:

* status summaries
* grant outcomes
* artefact links
* track-specific documentation
